# Sprint Packet - BudgetBrain

## Sprint Overview
Weekly sprint packet for BudgetBrain capstone project development.

## Sprint Artifacts
- Sprint Backlog
- Task Assignments
- Daily Standup Notes
- Sprint Review Documents
