## Team Workflow
1. Daily standup at 10:00 AM
2. Tasks tracked via GitHub Issues
3. Code reviews before merging
4. Weekly sprint reviews on Friday

## Definition of Done
- Code compiles without errors
- Feature works as specified
- UI matches design spec
- No regression in existing features
- README updated if needed
